<h2 id="510">5. Carrying out the group function</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Use the group function to send an email template, print address label or add a contact to a newsletter folder. This can be done simultaneously for one or multiple contacts.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Carrying out the group function:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>CRM » Contacts</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Search (<span class="icon "><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>) the contact(s) by means of the filter settings as described in the <a href="/en/crm/managing-contacts#200">Searching for a contact</a> chapter.<br>
→ The contacts that correspond to the search criteria entered are displayed.</p>
</li>
