<div class="title">Display of the primary invoice and delivery address</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>After you saved the primary invoice address and the primary delivery address, these addresses are directly displayed when opening the contact data record. You can find them on the right-hand side in the <strong>Addresses</strong> section. Click on <strong>Edit</strong> (<span class="icon yellow"><i class="fa fa-pencil  "></i></span>) to open the detail view of the address and to edit the address.<br></p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If neither an invoice address nor a delivery address was defined as primary address, the invoice address and the delivery address that were last added are displayed.</p>
</div>
