<strong><em>Note:</em></strong> The types <strong>Email</strong> and <strong>Telephone</strong> are statically displayed. Further available types in the drop-down list: VAT number, External address ID, Entry certificate, Post number, Personal ID, age rating, Birthday, Title, Contact person.</p></td>
</tr>
