<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1396">10.2. Creating tags for the messenger</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Go to <strong>Setup » Settings » Tags</strong> and create tags for the availability <strong>Messages</strong> so that they are available for the messenger.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>If you want to create messages that should be billed, you have to create tags for the availability <strong>Message (billable)</strong> in the same way. You have to add these tags to the message.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>How to create tags is described on the <a href="/en/basics/working-with-plentymarkets/tags">Tags</a> page of the manual.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="1400">10.3. Creating a message</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can save as many messages for your contacts as you like.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Creating a message:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
